FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common queries about our blockchain information discovery app
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What is the primary purpose of this app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app is designed to help users discover and stay updated on new blockchain information, including emerging projects, technologies, and trends in the crypto space.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: How does the app find new blockchain information?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: The app uses advanced algorithms and AI to scan multiple sources, including news outlets, social media, and blockchain networks, to identify and curate the latest and most relevant blockchain information for our users.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Is this app suitable for both beginners and experienced blockchain enthusiasts?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Absolutely! Our app caters to users of all levels. Beginners can learn about blockchain basics, while experienced users can dive deep into advanced topics and cutting-edge developments.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: How often is the information updated?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Our app updates information in real-time, ensuring that users always have access to the most current blockchain news and developments as they happen.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Can I customize the type of blockchain information I receive?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Yes, you can personalize your feed by selecting specific topics, projects, or technologies you're interested in. This allows you to focus on the blockchain information most relevant to your needs and interests.
